<p>In doing some research, I see that at level 20, rogues get the make poison skill.&nbsp;&nbsp;Is this a trade skill that you merely need to start doing (once you have the components)...or is this something that you have to train with a guild master first (i.e. invest a point)?  I went to the PoK guildmaster after I hit 20, but didn't have skill listed...didn't have time to look around yet.  Maybe in my home town? <br /> <br />Also, I keep seeing references to a rogue's ability to 'evade'...I take it this is some way to lose aggro after a big backstab....but I can't find this skill either.  Can someone help me here? <br /></p>
